Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:18.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我仍記得她眼角留下的那滴淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:18.10,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I still can remember the tear in her eye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:23.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}當他對我施咒\N並說了唯一一句「再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:23.05,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}when she cast her spell and\Nsaid nothing more than "goodbye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}記憶老去，臉也已記不清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.56,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The faces fade as the memories age
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:32.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}童年跟人生\N就這樣揮之而去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:32.36,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}A lifetime lost\Nand a childhood thrown away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:39.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}希望你在外面的世界\N能過得平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:39.70,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Best of luck to the world out there\Nand I hope you'll be okay
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:46.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}而我，\N也已經能接受，\N我在這邊的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:46.29,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Meanwhile,\NI'm feeling right at home\Nwith what I got around me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:52.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}要是，\N能沒人來煩我，\N我就能自己一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:52.95,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Seems like\NI would be all alone\Nif no one ever found me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我已經不想看到你，\N別來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.12,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}If you come looking around for me,\Nleave me be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:03.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因為我現在只需要\N我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:03.33,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}'cause the only friends I've got\Nare all I need
