Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.96,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The hunter finds his food for the night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:21.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}他技藝精湛，\N希望著今天的飯有著落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.96,0:01:21.61,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}with a quick-sharp aim\Nand a hunger from deep inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}小熊總是跟著熊媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.26,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The little bear goes where his mama will go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}熊媽媽也總\N確保小熊知道去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:31.25,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The mother bear goes\Nwhere the little cub knows to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:38.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}每個人在這世界\N都有自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:38.53,English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}The rest of them in the world out there\Nhave a different way of life
